(5, 'Bổ Gan Cà Gai Leo Plus', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Sản phẩm&lt;strong&gt; BỔ GAN C&amp;Agrave; GAI LEO PLUS&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;hỗ trợ đặc biệt &amp;nbsp;cho người bị vi&amp;ecirc;m gan si&amp;ecirc;u vi, nhất l&amp;agrave; vi&amp;ecirc;m gan si&amp;ecirc;u vi B m&amp;atilde;n t&amp;iacute;nh thể hoạt&amp;nbsp;động, gi&amp;uacute;p hỗ trợ điều trị&amp;nbsp;men gan cao, giảm triệu chứng của người bệnh gan, ph&amp;ograve;ng ngừa k&amp;igrave;m h&amp;atilde;m sự ph&amp;aacute;t&amp;nbsp;triển của xơ gan, ung thư gan, tăng miễn dịch cho gan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', '&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;width:750px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align:top; width:350px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I. GIỚI THIỆU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Gan l&amp;agrave; một trong những cơ quan lớn nhất của cơ&amp;nbsp;thể, đ&amp;oacute;ng một vai tr&amp;ograve; quan trọng&amp;nbsp;trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh&amp;nbsp;chuyển h&amp;oacute;a c&amp;aacute;c chất, l&amp;agrave;m v&amp;ocirc; hiệu h&amp;oacute;a c&amp;aacute;c&amp;nbsp;chất độc hại th&amp;acirc;m nhập&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave;o qua đường ti&amp;ecirc;u&amp;nbsp;ho&amp;aacute;, đồng thời l&amp;agrave;m giảm độc t&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave; thải trừ&amp;nbsp;một số chất cặn&amp;nbsp;b&amp;atilde;, độc hại do chuyển ho&amp;aacute; trong cơ thể tạo n&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;vertical-align:top; width:350px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top; width:370px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;II. TH&amp;Agrave;NH PHẦN:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Mỗi vi&amp;ecirc;n nang c&amp;oacute; chứa:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- C&amp;agrave; gai leo &amp;nbsp;....................................................1000mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Diệp hạ ch&amp;acirc;u ................................................. 500mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Bồ c&amp;ocirc;ng anh....................................................500mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Cardus marianus (Kế sữa)..............................75mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Linh chi...........................................................150mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Vitamin B1.......................................................0,5mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Vitamin B2.......................................................0,5mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Vitamin B6.......................................................0,5mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Vitamin PP.........................................................1mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- L-Arginine........................................................60mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Methionine........................................................25mg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Selen..................................................................5mcg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Phụ liệu: Tinh bột, magnesium stearate, talc vừa đủ 1 vi&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;hr /&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Lọ 60 vi&amp;ecirc;n nang&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top; width:50px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;vertical-align:top; width:350px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;III. C&amp;Ocirc;NG DỤNG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p tăng cường chức năng gan trong c&amp;aacute;c trường hợp:&amp;nbsp;Vi&amp;ecirc;m gan virus, xơ gan, men gan cao, gan nhiễm mỡ, vi&amp;ecirc;m gan cấp t&amp;iacute;nh, m&amp;atilde;n t&amp;iacute;nh, uống nhiều rượu bia, bị ngộ độc thực phẩm, ho&amp;aacute; chất.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p l&amp;agrave;m thuy&amp;ecirc;n giảm c&amp;aacute;c triệu chứng của bệnh gan như: Đau nhức hạn sườn, v&amp;agrave;ng da, dị ứng, mệt mỏi.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p tăng cường miễn dịch cơ thể, tăng cường chức năng giải độc của gan, gi&amp;uacute;p bảo vệ tế b&amp;agrave;o gan, hạn chế tổn thương tế b&amp;agrave;o gan do rượu, ho&amp;aacute; chất độc hại g&amp;acirc;y n&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IV. C&amp;Aacute;CH D&amp;Ugrave;NG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Uống 2 vi&amp;ecirc;n/lần, ng&amp;agrave;y d&amp;ugrave;ng 2 lần.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Mỗi đợt sử dụng từ 2-4 th&amp;aacute;ng v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; thể sử dụng nhắc lại &amp;nbsp;2-3 đợt trong năm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;V. ĐỐI TƯỢNG SỬ DỤNG:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Người c&amp;oacute; chức năng gan suy giảm do: Uống nhiều rượu bia, rối loạn chức năng gan, vi&amp;ecirc;m gan virus, vi&amp;ecirc;m gan B m&amp;atilde;n t&amp;iacute;nh, xơ gan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Người bị men gan cao, gan nhiễm mỡ, v&amp;agrave;ng da, mệt mỏi, đau tức hạ sườn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Lưu &amp;yacute;: Sản phẩm n&amp;agrave;y&amp;nbsp;kh&amp;ocirc;ng phải l&amp;agrave; thuốc v&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c dụng&amp;nbsp;thay thế thuốc chữa bệnh)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', 'bo-gan-ca-gai-leo-plus', 4, '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 662500, 0, '2015-10-01 20:13:03', '2015-10-13 02:42:27', 1, 0, 1, 1),
(6, 'Ích Phổi An Tâm', '&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Sản phẩm &lt;strong&gt;&amp;Iacute;CH PHỔI AN T&amp;Acirc;M &lt;/strong&gt;hỗ trợ cho người gặp c&amp;aacute;c vấn đề về h&amp;ocirc; hấp như&amp;nbsp;hen suyễn, ho l&amp;acirc;u, ho khan...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Tăng cường&amp;nbsp;miễn dịch cho cơ thể ngăn ngừa bệnh tật. Đặc biệt&amp;nbsp;ph&amp;ograve;ng ngừa loại bỏ c&amp;aacute;c khối u &amp;aacute;c t&amp;iacute;nh v&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;hỗ trợ điều trị ung thư.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', '&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;width:750px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;width:350px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I. GIỚI THIỆU:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Phổi&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;l&amp;agrave; một bộ phận trong cơ thể với vai tr&amp;ograve; ch&amp;iacute;nh yếu l&amp;agrave; trao đổi c&amp;aacute;c kh&amp;iacute;,&amp;nbsp;đem&amp;nbsp;&amp;ocirc;xy&amp;nbsp;từ kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute;&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave;o&amp;nbsp;tĩnh mạch&amp;nbsp;phổi&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;đi&amp;ocirc;xit cacbon từ&amp;nbsp;động mạch phổi ra ngo&amp;agrave;i. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra phổi cũng c&amp;oacute; một số khả năng thứ yếu kh&amp;aacute;c, gi&amp;uacute;p chuyển h&amp;oacute;a một v&amp;agrave;i chất sinh h&amp;oacute;a, lọc một số độc tố trong&amp;nbsp;m&amp;aacute;u. Phổi cũng l&amp;agrave; một nơi lưu trữ m&amp;aacute;u.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;4&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:250px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;II. TH&amp;Agrave;NH PHẦN:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Beta 1, 3 D glucan.........................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Nấm v&amp;acirc;n chi .................................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Ngũ vị tử.......................................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Trần b&amp;igrave; (vỏ qu&amp;yacute;t kh&amp;ocirc;)..................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Tinh chất mật ong........................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:30px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td style=&quot;width:300px&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;III. C&amp;Ocirc;NG DỤNG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;Tăng cường&amp;nbsp;hệ miễn dịch&amp;nbsp;để chống lại mọi bệnh tật v&amp;agrave; hạn chế tối đa nguy cơ nhiễm tr&amp;ugrave;ng&amp;nbsp;sau khi phẫu thuật.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Ph&amp;ograve;ng ngừa, loại bỏ c&amp;aacute;c khối u &amp;aacute;c t&amp;iacute;nh h&amp;igrave;nh th&amp;agrave;nh trong cơ thể.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ&amp;nbsp;trợ&amp;nbsp;giảm đau với mức độ nhất định&amp;nbsp;trong qu&amp;aacute; tr&amp;igrave;nh trị xạ v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;uacute;p&amp;nbsp;bệnh nh&amp;acirc;n ung thư nhanh ch&amp;oacute;ng phục hồi sức khoẻ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- &amp;nbsp;Hỗ trợ điều trị&amp;nbsp;hen suyễn, ho l&amp;acirc;u, ho khan, nhiều mồ h&amp;ocirc;i,&amp;nbsp;ra mồ h&amp;ocirc;i trộm, di tinh liệt dương v&amp;agrave; mệt mỏi biếng hoạt động&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p&amp;nbsp;k&amp;iacute;ch th&amp;iacute;ch ni&amp;ecirc;m mạc đường h&amp;ocirc; hấp, l&amp;agrave;m tăng dịch&amp;nbsp;tiết, l&amp;agrave;m lo&amp;atilde;ng đờm, gi&amp;atilde;n phế quản, hạ cơn hen,&amp;nbsp;ngăn chặn&amp;nbsp;cơn co&amp;nbsp;thắt phế quản&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p kh&amp;aacute;ng vi&amp;ecirc;m, chống lo&amp;eacute;t.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Lưu &amp;yacute;: Sản phẩm n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng phải l&amp;agrave; thuốc, kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c dụng thay thế thuốc chữa bệnh)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n', 'ich-phoi-an-tam', 4, '', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 1, 3, 662500, 0, '2015-10-05 06:00:46', '2015-10-14 06:44:07', 1, 0, 1, 1),
(7, 'Ích Não An Tâm', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Sản phẩm &lt;strong&gt;&amp;Iacute;CH N&amp;Atilde;O AN T&amp;Acirc;M&lt;/strong&gt; gi&amp;uacute;p hỗ trợ điều trị c&amp;aacute;c vấn đề suy giảm tr&amp;iacute; nhớ, tắc c&amp;aacute;c động, tĩnh mạch. Hỗ trợ điều trị về đường huyết v&amp;agrave; tim mạch.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', '&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;height:0px; width:750px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I. GIỚI THIỆU:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;N&amp;atilde;o người&amp;nbsp;l&amp;agrave; phần tr&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; trước nhất của hệ thần&amp;nbsp;kinh trung ương&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave; l&amp;agrave; cơ quan chủ yếu trong điều h&amp;agrave;nh hệ thần kinh ngoại vi.&amp;nbsp;B&amp;ecirc;n trong n&amp;atilde;o&amp;nbsp;l&amp;agrave; một hệ thống &amp;nbsp;mạng nơ-ron&amp;nbsp;phức tạp v&amp;agrave; một số tuyến nội tiết.&amp;nbsp;Một số&amp;nbsp;nơ-ron&amp;nbsp;tiếp nhận th&amp;ocirc;ng tin từ cơ thể (từ gi&amp;aacute;c quan: như &amp;nbsp;mắt, mũi, tai, lưỡi, da&amp;nbsp;từ&amp;nbsp;hệ thần kinh ngoại vi&amp;nbsp;v&amp;agrave; từ nhiều c&amp;aacute;c cơ quan kh&amp;aacute;c theo tuỷ sống&amp;nbsp;l&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;atilde;o); một số kh&amp;aacute;c c&amp;oacute; nhiệm vụ điều khiển tất cả c&amp;aacute;c cơ quan kh&amp;aacute;c của cơ thể (V&amp;iacute; dụ nhịp tim, nhịp thở, bắp thịt&amp;nbsp;tạo di chuyển,...). C&amp;aacute;c tuyến nội tiết trong n&amp;atilde;o tiếp nhận v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;oacute;ng th&amp;iacute;ch c&amp;aacute;c hormone&amp;nbsp;tạo li&amp;ecirc;n hệ chắt chẽ với c&amp;aacute;c tuyến nội tiết kh&amp;aacute;c trong cơ thể.&amp;nbsp;N&amp;atilde;o c&amp;ograve;n c&amp;oacute; chức năng tạo những hoạt động cao cấp như &amp;nbsp;suy nghĩ, t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n, ph&amp;aacute;n x&amp;eacute;t, trừu tượng, tưởng tượng, v.v....&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;II. TH&amp;Agrave;NH PHẦN:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;TAURINE.............................................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;C&amp;Acirc;Y THẠCH T&amp;Ugrave;NG RĂNG CƯA...................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;BẠCH QUẢ..........................................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- ĐAN S&amp;Acirc;M............................................................&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;III. C&amp;Ocirc;NG DỤNG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trợ thị lực v&amp;agrave;&amp;nbsp;hỗ trợ chống lại&amp;nbsp;bệnh đục nh&amp;atilde;n mắt li&amp;ecirc;n quan đến tuổi t&amp;aacute;c.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trợ điều trị bệnh tim mạch.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Gi&amp;uacute;p cơ xương hoạt động b&amp;igrave;nh thường, gi&amp;uacute;p lợi tiểu.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trợ điều trị c&amp;aacute;c bệnh rối loạn về tr&amp;iacute; nhớ.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trợ tốt cho đường huyết, hỗ trợ điều trị c&amp;aacute;c vấn đề về tim mạch.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trơ điều trị những rối loạn ở&amp;nbsp;tai trong như điếc, ch&amp;oacute;ng mặt v&amp;agrave; &amp;ugrave; tai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Lưu &amp;yacute;: Sản phẩm kh&amp;ocirc;ng phải l&amp;agrave; thuốc, kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c dụng thay thế thuốc chữa bệnh)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', 'ich-nao-an-tam', 4, '', '', '', 1, 0, 0, 1, 2, 662500, 0, '2015-10-05 06:02:42', '2015-10-14 06:43:59', 1, 0, 1, 1),
(8, 'Bổ Xương Khớp', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Sản phẩm &lt;strong&gt;BỔ XƯƠNG KHỚP&lt;/strong&gt; hỗ trợ điều trị người gặp vấn đề về xương khớp như: Tho&amp;aacute;i ho&amp;aacute; sụn khớp, kh&amp;ocirc; khớp, phong thấp đau nhức xương, vi&amp;ecirc;m khớp ...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', '&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;10&quot; style=&quot;width:750px&quot;&gt;\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td colspan=&quot;3&quot;&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I. GIỚI THIỆU:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Bệnh xương khớp v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c triệu&amp;nbsp;chứng đau nhức xương khớp&amp;nbsp;thường gặp ở phụ nữ tuổi trung ni&amp;ecirc;n v&amp;agrave; người cao tuổi, c&amp;aacute;c triệu chứng r&amp;otilde; rệt hơn khi thay đổi thời tiết v&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave;o&amp;nbsp;m&amp;ugrave;a lạnh.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n		&lt;tr&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;II. TH&amp;Agrave;NH PHẦN:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Glucosamine.............................................400mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-&amp;nbsp;MSM (Methylsulfonylmethane)...............50mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;-&lt;strong&gt; Độc hoạt....................................................100mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Ngưu tất....................................................100mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Ph&amp;ograve;ng phong............................................200mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Xuy&amp;ecirc;n khung..............................................50mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Cốt to&amp;aacute;i bổ..................................................50mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- Chondroitin................................................10mg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;Phụ liệu: Magnesium stearate, talc vừa đủ 1 vi&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;*&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute;:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;+&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;Sản phẩm n&amp;agrave;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng g&amp;acirc;y rối loạn ruột, dạ d&amp;agrave;y n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;oacute; thể d&amp;ugrave;ng l&amp;acirc;u d&amp;agrave;i.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;+ Sản phẩm c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c động l&amp;ecirc;n nguy&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;acirc;n g&amp;acirc;y tho&amp;aacute;i h&amp;oacute;a khớp. Do đ&amp;oacute;, t&amp;aacute;c dụng c&amp;oacute; thể biểu hiện chậm sau khoảng 1 tuần sử dụng.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;+ Thận trọng cho phụ nữ c&amp;oacute; thai v&amp;agrave; cho con b&amp;uacute;.&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n			&lt;td&gt;\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;III. C&amp;Ocirc;NG DỤNG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;- &lt;/strong&gt;Gi&amp;uacute;p phục hồi, t&amp;aacute;i tạo m&amp;ocirc; sụn khớp, tăng tiết dịch khớp, đảm bảo sự vận động linh hoạt của khớp, giảm đau, b&amp;ocirc;i trơn khớp.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Hỗ trợ liệu ph&amp;aacute;p điều trị tho&amp;aacute;i h&amp;oacute;a khớp, đau mỏi khớp.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;IV. ĐỐI TƯỢNG SỬ DỤNG:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Người tho&amp;aacute;i h&amp;oacute;a xương khớp, đau mỏi khớp, đau nhức xương khớp.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;V. C&amp;Aacute;CH D&amp;Ugrave;NG:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Người lớn: Uống 2 vi&amp;ecirc;n/lần x 2 lần/ng&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;- Để c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c dụng hiệu quả n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng trong 6-8 tuần, mỗi năm c&amp;oacute; thể uống lặp lại 2-3 lần.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n			&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n			&lt;/td&gt;\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\n&lt;/table&gt;\n\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:times new roman,times,serif&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;(Lưu &amp;yacute;: Sản phẩm kh&amp;ocirc;ng phải l&amp;agrave; thuốc, kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&amp;aacute;c dụng thay thế thuốc chữa bệnh)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n', 'bo-xuong-khop', 4, 'Sản phẩm BỔ XƯƠNG KHỚP hỗ trợ điều trị người gặp vấn đề về xương khớp như: Thoái hoá sụn khớp, khô khớp, phong thấp đau nhức xương, viêm khớp ', '', '', 1, 1, 0, 1, 4, 662500, 0, '2015-10-05 06:12:56', '2015-10-22 07:31:56', 1, 0, 1, 1);

